{"lemma":"خَرَزِ","slug":"خَرَزِ","root":"خ.ر.ز","root_slug":"خ-ر-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ر-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10312","n10313"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%B2%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bore into, to pierce"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"beads","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of خُرْزَة (ḵurza, “suture”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10312","headword_ar":"خَرَزَ","root":"xrz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarozN","text_ar":"خَرْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sewed"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, TA) a skin, or hide, (Msb, TA,) or a boot, &c. (S, A, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalaAmu fulaAnK","text_ar":"كَلَامُ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaxarozi AlA_imaA='i","text_ar":"كَخَرْزِ الاـِمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"[The language of such a one is like the female slaves' sewing of skins];"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., [its ornaments, lit.] its pearls, and its cowries, are far apart. (A, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n10313","headword_ar":"خَرَزٌ","root":"xrz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[a coll. gen. n.,] a word of well-known meaning, (Msb,) [i.e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beads;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are strung:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is hung"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"things that are hung"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the neck, made of coloured stone, red and green:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 431:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gems,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similar stones,"},{"kind":"text","text":"both"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) [also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"factitious gems,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusayofisaA='u","text_ar":"فُسَيْفِسَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as explained in the K &c:)] n. un."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazapN","text_ar":"خَرَزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) the latter signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"[a single bead;] what is strung:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and also, (i.e. the latter,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gem,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precious stone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for instance]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as is set in a ring, whether good or bad:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. of the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazaAtN","text_ar":"خَرَزَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazaAtu Almaliki","text_ar":"خَرَزَاتُ المَلِكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almuloki","text_ar":"المُلْكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The gems of the king's crown:"},{"kind":"text","text":"when the king had reigned a year, a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazap","text_ar":"خَرَزَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"was added to his crown, in order that the number of the years of his reign might be known: (S, K:) such is said to have been the case. (S.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uwtiYa xarazaAti Almuloki sit~iyna Hij~apF","text_ar":"اُوتِىَ خَرَزَاتِ المُلْكِ سِتِّينَ حِجَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:) [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He reigned sixty years:"},{"kind":"text","text":"lit.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he received the gems of the crown sixty years"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazapu","text_ar":"خَرَزَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEayoni","text_ar":"العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadaqap","text_ar":"حَدَقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lens"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the eye."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hdq","text_ar":"حدق"},{"kind":"text","text":") ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazN","text_ar":"خَرَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied to The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small shells called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wadaE","text_ar":"وَدَع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S* and K* and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wdE","text_ar":"ودع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-  It also signifies (tropical:) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vertebræ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the back, (S, A, TA,) and of the neck: each one is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazapN","text_ar":"خَرَزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": which latter is also explained as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is between two vertebræ."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","JK","K","TA","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}